snippet.title: The Choreographist - Dance Move Suggestions
snippet.description:
In the making of The Choreographist, we really wanted to make attacks feel like dance moves. But... Danny didn't feel like he explained things well.

And so. This is how Danny provided guidance. It is not useful. Don't be like Danny. Be better.
